---
description: Core CloserOS engineering and agent workflow rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` and `PROJECT_STATUS.md` before material changes.

Follow task IDs in `TASKS.md`. Work on one task at a time.

Never:
- fabricate provider behavior;
- claim production readiness without the release gate;
- log or commit secrets or customer data;
- send raw personal data to an external LLM;
- bypass tenant authorization;
- implement autonomous outbound messaging in the initial release;
- introduce microservices or Kubernetes without an accepted ADR.

Before completion, run applicable formatting, linting, type checks, tests, and update `PROJECT_STATUS.md`.
